{"tid":1299961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★HK Yes IT! 國泰稱會從世界各地招攬資訊科技人才","createTime":"2019-07-09T08:19:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T03:26:14.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"86f8e3f03a668fad76bae3ddbe71f62f666113ca","tid":1299961,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:19:11.000Z","msg":"國泰航空顧客及商務總裁盧家培表示，會從世界各地招攬資訊科技人才，集團制定不同科技創新計劃，為在學人士提供暑期實習，讓政府、大學、創業公司攜手合作，使香港成為技術和創新的領先樞紐。<br />\n<br />\n他在一個論壇上提到，國泰3年前逐步將應用程式轉移到雲端，亦利用自動回覆機械人在颱風季節提升處理查詢的效率，減少前線員工工作量。<br />\n<br />\n他又提到，國泰在商務艙增加平板電腦，乘客可以透過平板電腦下單，提高效率同乘客滿意度，前線員工壓力亦相應下降。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467411-20190709.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467411-20190709.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=R%2BBR62t8sBL7FL0rmd5Y1bTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=9b384185\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467411-20190709.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=698a7b8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467411-20190709.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"48717c70622b8267a3ccd9b1430c924f082075ed","tid":1299961,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f636d2e306ded6db4c3b4a6b17f1048d23468fec","tid":1299961,"uid":8219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:33:01.000Z","msg":"招攬完再炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71df9f17b05dd8015492a3c90e376b9dcc86f2d0","tid":1299961,"uid":54125,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:35:29.000Z","msg":"通常世界各地=鄰國"},{"pid":"2c66b8ed931edb1c1ba1b71a176d99068c17c681","tid":1299961,"uid":19